text: Phwk khea (yin) thangan hı khea (su lay man) tam thi khea txngkar (chen srang) prasath hlay hæng thi sung trahngan læa brrda hun calxng læa brrda khom sı xahar mi khnad thea bxna læa brrda hmx sahrab hung xahar tang xyu kab thi phwk cea cng thangan theid wngswan khx ngdawud xey! Dwy kar khxbkhun læa swn nxy hæng pwng baw khxng rea thi pen phu khxbkhun
